title: #92Noon Live from TCO: Gibson / Reynolds / Birk / Kendricks
description: The FAN's Paul Allen and Eric Nordquist discuss Twins-Yankees with Kyle Gibson and Harold Reynolds, tune into the Mike Zimmer and Kirk Cousins Wednesday press conferences, and then break it all down with Matt Birk and Eric Kendricks.
